[22:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'And then of course there\'s Keet, which I\'ve I believe I\'ve mentioned. Um really really good app. One other thing I\'ll say about Keet is um when you go on a video call in Keet, and'

[22:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'you have a video call with someone, you\'re kind of like, "Wow. I didn\'t realize I\'ve been living my life at such low resolution." It\'s sort of like when you have Italian'

